      <h1>Community energy groups have achieved amazing things</h1>
      <p>Community energy groups have been pioneers in a number of ways. Groups have demonstrated a superior model of financing green projects, without the need for banks or big corporations.</p>
      <p>Groups have made immediate environmental benefit, generating renewable energy to power thousands of homes.</p>
      <p>Perhaps most importantly, community energy groups have got people excited and engaged in a better, low carbon future. By just getting on with it, they’ve shifted the narrative away from doom and gloom, showing communities that they can make a difference.</p>
